title: United Kingdom Imports of Miscellaneous Chemical Products
description: Imports of Miscellaneous Chemical Products in the United Kingdom decreased to 545.12 GBP Million in September from 606.67 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Miscellaneous Chemical Products in the United Kingdom averaged 302.06 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1360.75 GBP Million in January of 2022 and a record low of 128.07 GBP Million in December of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Miscellaneous Chemical Products.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
